# ✅ KEEP THESE FILES (DO NOT IGNORE):
# - pubspec.yaml (dependencies)
# - README.md (documentation)
# - ARCHITECTURE.md (project structure)
# - FEATURES.md (feature list)
# - lib/ (source code)
# - assets/ (essential app assets only)
# - android/ (source config only, no build)
# - ios/ (source config only, no build)
# - web/ (source config only, no build)
# - linux/ (source config only, no build)
# - macos/ (source config only, no build)
# - windows/ (source config only, no build)
